          "description": "The pharmacy cashier (a black heavy set female) was extremely rude to me and I just decided to not continue my purchase with her and that I was going to complete my purchase at self check out so she yelled at me and said \"you have to buy that before you leave the store,\" as if I were going to steal it.\nShe and the store manager refused to give me her name so I could not make a complaint, but I called and made the complaint already.\nPeople like that shouldn't be working behind store counters.\nIt's terrible how this store manager doesn't hire the right people.\nTo run a business and keep the customers coming back,  you have to be good with them and hire people who know how to interact with the public.\nI could see this store going out of business and hoping it does!!",
